data.meta_description: Eventbrite - Murphy Arts District presents Justin Moore and Joe Nichols - Saturday, August 31, 2024 at MAD Amphitheater, El Dorado, AR. Find event and ticket information.
data.text:
Come see Justin Moore and Joe Nichols live!

Get ready for a night of country music like no other at the MAD Amphitheater. Join us on Sat Aug 31 2024 at 8:00 PM for an unforgettable concert featuring two of the biggest names in the industry.

Justin Moore and Joe Nichols will be taking the stage to perform all their hits, so grab your friends and family for a night you won't want to miss. Make sure to get your tickets early as this event is sure to sell out fast!
